essage-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="9f3cfcef-4f1a-474e-9ef1-c65d68b460c1" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="81">Sure Merin 😊<br data-start="13" data-end="16">
Upload all the seminar reference papers you selected last year.</p>
<p data-start="83" data-end="113">After you upload them, I will:</p>
<p data-start="115" data-end="300">✔ Read each paper<br data-start="132" data-end="135">
✔ Suggest the <strong data-start="149" data-end="161">best two</strong> for a comparative study<br data-start="185" data-end="188" data-is-only-node="">
✔ Explain <strong data-start="198" data-end="223">why they are suitable</strong><br data-start="223" data-end="226">
✔ Help you prepare the <strong data-start="249" data-end="271">comparison outline</strong> and <strong data-start="276" data-end="300">seminar report draft</strong></p>
