<h1 data-start="456" data-end="493">🎯 What I will prepare for you now:</h1>
<p data-start="495" data-end="554">I can create your <strong data-start="513" data-end="542">full rough seminar report</strong>, including:</p>
<h3 data-start="556" data-end="574">✔ Title Page</h3>
<h3 data-start="575" data-end="591">✔ Abstract</h3>
<h3 data-start="592" data-end="612">✔ Introduction</h3>
<h3 data-start="613" data-end="639">✔ Summary of Paper 1</h3>
<h3 data-start="640" data-end="666">✔ Summary of Paper 2</h3>
<h3 data-start="667" data-end="738">✔ Comparison (Algorithms, Input, Application, Scope, Limitations)</h3>
<h3 data-start="739" data-end="764">✔ Comparative Table</h3>
<h3 data-start="765" data-end="783">✔ Conclusion</h3>
<h3 data-start="784" data-end="821">✔ References (formatted properly)</h3>
<hr data-start="823" data-end="826">
<h1 data-start="828" data-end="892">❓ Do you want me to prepare the full rough seminar report now?</h1>
<p data-start="894" data-end="903">Just say:</p>
<h3 data-start="905" data-end="946"><strong data-start="909" data-end="946">“Yes, prepare my seminar report.”</strong></h3>
