d="f894fef1-d2ec-4e9e-bb42-c4cafe1e6c74" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="145">Perfect Merin! 😊<br data-start="17" data-end="20">
I will prepare your <strong data-start="40" data-end="117">full seminar paper exactly like the sample (two-column IEEE-style layout)</strong> based on the comparison of:</p>
<h3 data-start="147" data-end="162">✔ Paper 1</h3>
<p data-start="163" data-end="174">✔ Paper 2</p>
<p data-start="176" data-end="269">But before I generate the full formatted seminar paper PDF,<br data-start="235" data-end="238">
I need <strong data-start="245" data-end="268">one detail from you</strong>:</p>
<hr data-start="271" data-end="274">
<h1 data-start="276" data-end="330">⭐ <strong data-start="280" data-end="330">What title do you want for your seminar paper?</strong></h1>
<p data-start="332" data-end="401">Here are some title options (you can choose one or tell me your own):</p>
<h3 data-start="403" data-end="420">🔹 Option A</h3>
<p data-start="421" data-end="495"><strong data-start="421" data-end="495">A Comparative Study on AI Techniques and Applications in Cybersecurity</strong></p>
<h3 data-start="497" data-end="514">🔹 Option B</h3>
<p data-start="515" data-end="601"><strong data-start="515" data-end="601">Comparative Analysis of Artificial Intelligence Approaches in Modern Cybersecurity</strong></p>
<h3 data-start="603" data-end="620">🔹 Option C</h3>
<p data-start="621" data-end="681"><strong data-start="621" data-end="681">A Review and Comparison of AI-Based Cybersecurity Models</strong></p>
<h3 data-start="683" data-end="700">🔹 Option D</h3>
<p data-start="701" data-end="777"><strong data-start="701" data-end="777">AI in Cybersecurity: A Comparative Review of Two Recent Research Studies</strong></p>
<hr data-start="779" data-end="782">
<h3 data-start="784" data-end="842">👉 Tell me the <strong data-start="803" data-end="821">title you want</strong>, and I will prepare:</h3>
<p data-start="844" data-end="1139">✔ Title page<br data-start="856" data-end="859">
✔ Abstract<br data-start="869" data-end="872">
✔ Introduction<br data-start="886" data-end="889">
✔ Summary of Paper 1<br data-start="909" data-end="912">
✔ Summary of Paper 2<br data-start="932" data-end="935">
✔ Comparative analysis (algorithms, input, applications, limitations…)<br data-start="1005" data-end="1008">
✔ Comparison table<br data-start="1026" data-end="1029">
✔ Figures if needed<br data-start="1048" data-end="1051">
✔ Conclusion<br data-start="1063" data-end="1066">
✔ References<br data-start="1078" data-end="1081">
✔ Proper seminar paper format (two-column like the sample)</p>
<hr data-start="1141" data-end="1144">
