 relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="67">Sure Merin! Here is a <strong data-start="22" data-end="66">short, clean abstract with 4–5 sentences</strong>:</p>
<hr data-start="69" data-end="72">
<h3 data-start="74" data-end="111"><strong data-start="78" data-end="109">📌 Abstract (Short Version)</strong></h3>
<p data-start="112" data-end="771">Artificial Intelligence (AI) plays a major role in improving cybersecurity by enabling faster, more accurate threat detection and response. This paper presents a comparative study of two research works that discuss AI techniques and their applications in cybersecurity. The first paper explains the impact and limitations of AI, while the second highlights recent advancements and real-world uses. The comparison focuses on algorithms, input parameters, application areas, strengths, and challenges of both studies. The findings show that AI is essential for modern security systems but still requires improvements in accuracy, data handling, and ethical use.</p>
