words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-mini"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="191">Perfect Merin! 🌟<br data-start="17" data-end="20">
Here’s a <strong data-start="29" data-end="57">well-organized structure</strong> for your seminar paper based on your two selected papers (Paper 1 &amp; Paper 2). You can use this to directly create your Word document:</p>
<hr data-start="193" data-end="196">
<h2 data-start="198" data-end="231"><strong data-start="201" data-end="231">Seminar Paper Organization</strong></h2>
<h3 data-start="233" data-end="249"><strong data-start="237" data-end="247">Title:</strong></h3>
<p data-start="250" data-end="322"><em data-start="250" data-end="322">A Comparative Study on AI Techniques and Applications in Cybersecurity</em></p>
<h3 data-start="324" data-end="342"><strong data-start="328" data-end="340">Abstract</strong></h3>
<p data-start="343" data-end="398">4–5 sentences summarizing the paper (already prepared).</p>
<h3 data-start="400" data-end="418"><strong data-start="404" data-end="416">Keywords</strong></h3>
<p data-start="419" data-end="580">Artificial Intelligence (AI), Cybersecurity, Machine Learning, Threat Detection, Anomaly Detection, Predictive Analytics, Automated Response, Security Algorithms</p>
<h3 data-start="582" data-end="607"><strong data-start="586" data-end="605">1. Introduction</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="608" data-end="761">
<li data-start="608" data-end="645">
<p data-start="610" data-end="645">Importance of AI in cybersecurity</p>
</li>
<li data-start="646" data-end="685">
<p data-start="648" data-end="685">Growing challenges of cyber threats</p>
</li>
<li data-start="686" data-end="723">
<p data-start="688" data-end="723">Purpose of this comparative study</p>
</li>
<li data-start="724" data-end="761">
<p data-start="726" data-end="761">Overview of the two selected papers</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="763" data-end="794"><strong data-start="767" data-end="792">2. Summary of Paper 1</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="795" data-end="947">
<li data-start="795" data-end="834">
<p data-start="797" data-end="834">Title, authors, publication details</p>
</li>
<li data-start="835" data-end="854">
