<p data-start="857" data-end="893">AI techniques/algorithms discussed</p>
</li>
<li data-start="894" data-end="917">
<p data-start="896" data-end="917">Application domains</p>
</li>
<li data-start="918" data-end="947">
<p data-start="920" data-end="947">Strengths and limitations</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="949" data-end="980"><strong data-start="953" data-end="978">3. Summary of Paper 2</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="981" data-end="1133">
<li data-start="981" data-end="1020">
<p data-start="983" data-end="1020">Title, authors, publication details</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1021" data-end="1040">
<p data-start="1023" data-end="1040">Main objectives</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1041" data-end="1079">
<p data-start="1043" data-end="1079">AI techniques/algorithms discussed</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1080" data-end="1103">
