<hr data-start="2533" data-end="2536">
<p data-start="2538" data-end="2710">This <strong data-start="2543" data-end="2567">Comparative Analysis</strong> provides a <strong data-start="2579" data-end="2600">side-by-side view</strong> of the two papers, making it easy for your seminar report to clearly show the differences and similarities.</p>
<hr data-start="2712" data-end="2715">
<p data-start="2717" data-end="2831">If you want, I can now <strong data-start="2740" data-end="2774">write the “Conclusion” section</strong> as well so your report is almost ready for submission.</p>
