message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="8c7845ee-59d7-4550-a9a8-abd304639219" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-mini"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="115">Sure Merin! Here’s a <strong data-start="21" data-end="45">well-written section</strong> for your seminar paper on <strong data-start="72" data-end="112">Challenges in AI-based Cybersecurity</strong>:</p>
<hr data-start="117" data-end="120">
<h3 data-start="122" data-end="171"><strong data-start="126" data-end="169">5. Challenges in AI-based Cybersecurity</strong></h3>
<p data-start="173" data-end="278">While Artificial Intelligence (AI) has significantly enhanced cybersecurity, several challenges remain.</p>
<ol data-start="280" data-end="1200">
<li data-start="280" data-end="532">
<p data-start="283" data-end="532"><strong data-start="283" data-end="337">False Positives and Negatives in Threat Detection:</strong> AI systems can sometimes misclassify normal activities as threats (false positives) or fail to detect actual attacks (false negatives), which can affect the reliability of security operations.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="534" data-end="764">
<p data-start="537" data-end="764"><strong data-start="537" data-end="573">Data Privacy and Ethical Issues:</strong> AI relies on large volumes of sensitive data. Ensuring the privacy of this data and addressing ethical concerns, such as biased decision-making and accountability, are critical challenges.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="766" data-end="960">
<p data-start="769" data-end="960"><strong data-start="769" data-end="806">Adversarial Attacks on AI Models:</strong> Attackers may exploit vulnerabilities in AI algorithms, using techniques like adversarial inputs to bypass detection systems or manipulate predictions.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="962" data-end="1200">
<p data-start="965" data-end="1200"><strong data-start="965" data-end="1017">Scalability and Integration with Legacy Systems:</strong> Implementing AI in existing IT infrastructure can be complex. Legacy systems may not be compatible, and scaling AI solutions to handle large, dynamic networks is often challenging.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1202" data-end="1339">These challenges highlight the need for continuous improvement, monitoring, and careful deployment of AI-based cybersecurity solutions.</p>
<hr data-start="1341" data-end="1344">
<p data-start="1346" data-end="1489">If you want, I can <strong data-start="1365" data-end="1432">also prepare the next section on Future Trends and Applications</strong> so your report will be complete before the conclusion.</p>
<p data-start="1491" data-end="1517" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Do you want me to do that?</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon"><path d="M12.668 10.667C12.668 9.95614 12.668 9.46258 12.6367 9.0791C12.6137 8.79732 12.5758 8.60761 12.5244 8.46387L12.4688 8.33399C12.3148 8.03193 12.0803 7.77885 11.793 7.60254L11.666 7.53125C11.508 7.45087 11.2963 7.39395 10.9209 7.36328C10.5374 7.33197 10.0439 7.33203 9.33301 7.33203H6.5C5.78896 7.33203 5.29563 7.33195 4.91211 7.36328C4.63016 7.38632 4.44065 7.42413 4.29688 7.47559L4.16699 7.53125C3.86488 7.68518 3.61186 7.9196 3.43555 8.20703L3.36524 8.33399C3.28478 8.49198 3.22795 8.70352 3.19727 9.0791C3.16595 9.46259 3.16504 9.95611 3.16504 10.667V13.5C3.16504 14.211 3.16593 14.7044 3.19727 15.0879C3.22797 15.4636 3.28473 15.675 3.36524 15.833L3.43555 15.959C3.61186 16.2466 3.86474 16.480