ssage-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="9ea9c0fd-268a-42e8-90db-e7ccbf95daf0" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-mini"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="109">Sure Merin! Here’s a <strong data-start="21" data-end="45">well-written section</strong> for your seminar paper on <strong data-start="72" data-end="106">Future Trends and Applications</strong>:</p>
<hr data-start="111" data-end="114">
<h3 data-start="116" data-end="159"><strong data-start="120" data-end="157">6. Future Trends and Applications</strong></h3>
<p data-start="161" data-end="291">The role of Artificial Intelligence (AI) in cybersecurity is rapidly evolving, with several promising trends shaping the future:</p>
<ol data-start="293" data-end="1415">
<li data-start="293" data-end="636">
<p data-start="296" data-end="636"><strong data-start="296" data-end="357">AI Integration with IoT, Blockchain, and Cloud Computing:</strong> AI is being increasingly integrated with emerging technologies to enhance security. In IoT networks, AI can detect anomalies across connected devices. Blockchain provides secure and tamper-proof data handling, while cloud computing allows scalable AI-based security solutions.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="638" data-end="935">
<p data-start="641" data-end="935"><strong data-start="641" data-end="704">Predictive Cybersecurity and Real-time Threat Intelligence:</strong> AI enables predictive analytics to anticipate potential cyber threats before they occur. Real-time monitoring and analysis allow organizations to respond instantly to security incidents, reducing damage and improving resilience.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="937" data-end="1173">
<p data-start="940" data-end="1173"><strong data-start="940" data-end="999">Use of Generative AI for Threat Simulation and Testing:</strong> Generative AI models can simulate potential cyber-attacks to test system vulnerabilities, helping organizations prepare for unknown threats and improve defense mechanisms.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1175" data-end="1415">
<p data-start="1178" data-end="1415"><strong data-start="1178" data-end="1219">Autonomous Incident Response Systems:</strong> Advanced AI systems can automate threat mitigation, isolate affected systems, and perform recovery operations with minimal human intervention, increasing efficiency and reducing response times.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1417" data-end="1612">These trends indicate that AI will continue to play a central role in creating adaptive, intelligent, and proactive cybersecurity systems capable of handling increasingly sophisticated attacks.</p>
<hr data-start="1614" data-end="1617">
<p data-start="1619" data-end="1853">If you want, I can now <strong data-start="1642" data-end="1664">compile everything</strong>—Abstract, Keywords, Introduction, Literature Survey, Comparative Analysis, Challenges, Future Trends, Conclusion, References—into a <strong data-start="1797" data-end="1829">complete Word seminar report</strong> ready for submission.</p>
<p data-start="1855" data-end="1886" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Do you want me to do that next?</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon"><path d="M12.668 10.667C12.668 9.95614 12.668 9.46258 12.6367 9.0791C12.6137 8.79732 12.5758 8.60761 12.5244 8.46387L12.4688 8.33399C12.3148 8.03193 12.0803 7.77885 11.793 7.60254L11.666 7.53125C11.508 7.45087 11.2963 7.39395 10.9209 7.36328C10.5374 7.33197 10.0439 7.33203 9.33301 7.33203H6.5C5.78896 7.33203 5.29563 7.33195 4.91211 7.36328C4.63016 7.38632 4.44065 7.42413 4.29688 7.47559L4.16699 7.53125C3.86488 7.68518 3.61186 7.9196 3.43555 8.20703L3.36524 8.33399C3.28478 8.49198 3.22795 8.70352 3.19727 9.0791C3.16595 9.46259 3.16504 9.95611 3.16504 10.667V13.5C3.16504 14.211 3.16593 14.7044 3.19727 15.0879C3.22797 15.4636 3.28473 15.675 3.36524 15.833L3.43555 15.959C3.61186 16.2466 3.86474 1